WEBVTT

00:29.521 --> 00:32.161
<b>Yo, Sasaki.</b>

00:32.611 --> 00:34.911
<b>Hey, what's up?</b>

00:35.771 --> 00:37.311
<b>The heck, man?</b>

00:37.311 --> 00:41.081
<b>I looked all over for you 'cuz you weren't
in the smoking lounge downstairs.</b>

00:41.591 --> 00:44.931
<b>Oh, my bad. Did you need me for something?</b>

00:53.971 --> 00:56.241
<b>The chief wants to have 
a meeting in a few.</b>

00:57.571 --> 00:58.351
<b>Sheesh.</b>

00:59.611 --> 01:04.871
<b>Here we go with another pointless meeting 
that goes on and on and on and on and on.</b>

01:05.541 --> 01:06.701
<b>Now, now.</b>

01:08.011 --> 01:09.741
<b>Man...</b>

01:15.271 --> 01:17.971
<b>I just wanna go home already.</b>

01:23.931 --> 01:25.661
<b>I feel you.</b>

03:03.061 --> 03:06.561
<b>Genki Trading</b>

03:18.531 --> 03:24.201
<b>Souvenirs</b>

03:18.531 --> 03:24.201
<b>go here</b>

03:39.761 --> 03:41.971
<b>Local</b>

04:33.271 --> 04:34.941
<b>24-Hour</b>

04:33.271 --> 04:34.941
<b>Supermarket S</b>

04:53.671 --> 04:55.541
<b>Free Ice
For Preservation</b>

04:57.291 --> 05:00.541
<b>Free Ice
For Preservation</b>

05:00.551 --> 05:14.191
<b></b>Alcohol Corner

05:19.571 --> 05:23.981
<b>Yummy Mochi Chips</b>

05:24.821 --> 05:26.621
<b>Thank you! Come again!</b>

05:29.201 --> 05:30.571
<b>Welcome!</b>

05:33.071 --> 05:35.361
<b>Do you have your loyalty point card?</b>

05:35.361 --> 05:37.211
<b>I do, yes.</b>

05:37.801 --> 05:39.091
<b>Thank you.</b>

05:40.931 --> 05:42.911
<b>Here's your card back.</b>

05:49.341 --> 05:51.601
<b>Would you like a bag?</b>

05:52.231 --> 05:53.781
<b>I'll take a three-yen one, please.</b>

05:53.781 --> 05:57.731
<b>That'll be 883 yen in total.</b>

05:57.731 --> 05:58.731
<b>Here.</b>

06:06.691 --> 06:09.011
<b>Here's your change and receipt.</b>

06:10.181 --> 06:11.081
<b>Thanks.</b>

06:14.041 --> 06:15.721
<b>Thank you! Come again!</b>

06:20.501 --> 06:22.761
<b>Served By: Yamada</b>

06:23.021 --> 06:25.141
<b><i>Yamada-san at register two...</i></b>

06:26.011 --> 06:28.641
<b><i>She's my post-work chill pill.</i></b>

06:31.091 --> 06:32.521
<b><i>That said...</i></b>

06:33.521 --> 06:37.331
<b><i>I've been going too often lately, 
even when I don't need anything.</i></b>

06:37.331 --> 06:39.771
<b><i>What a stupid waste of money.</i></b>

06:40.271 --> 06:43.381
<b><i>Maybe I should try offering it 
to Yamada-san as a gift.</i></b>

06:43.741 --> 06:45.741
<b><i>You never know. Might make her happy.</i></b>

06:45.731 --> 06:49.451
<b>Yummy Mochi Chips</b>

06:46.421 --> 06:49.091
<b><i>Wow! Thank you so much!</i></b>

06:52.841 --> 06:58.131
<b><i>I sound like one of those delusional 
middle-aged criminals on the news.</i></b>

06:58.921 --> 07:02.421
<b>Genki Trading</b>

06:59.271 --> 07:02.421
<b>What is the meaning of this, Sasaki-kun?!</b>

07:02.421 --> 07:06.681
<b>Do you think "doing your rounds" 
just means going on a leisurely stroll?!</b>

07:06.681 --> 07:10.731
<b>I swear! It is unacceptable 
that you didn't let me know!</b>

07:10.731 --> 07:12.311
<b>I apologize, sir.</b>

07:12.311 --> 07:15.941
<b>You need to work on your 
communication, big-time!</b>

07:15.941 --> 07:18.201
<b>You're making me look bad 
as your manager—</b>

07:18.201 --> 07:22.321
<b>Sorry for interrupting, Chief, 
but Eda-san of Shikaku Inc.</b>

07:22.681 --> 07:24.961
<b>wants to know if the estimate is ready.</b>

07:24.961 --> 07:28.201
<b>Ack! Tell him I'll send it over tomorrow!</b>

07:29.291 --> 07:31.771
<b>We apologize for keeping you waiting!</b>

07:31.771 --> 07:33.161
<b>Yes, we'll send it over tomorrow!</b>

07:33.161 --> 07:35.541
<b>Of course! We're terribly sorry!</b>

07:34.571 --> 07:36.581
<b>We're having a meeting at 7 PM!</b>

07:41.981 --> 07:44.661
<b><i>That moronic boss of mine...</i></b>

07:45.061 --> 07:47.281
<b><i>It's bad enough that 
the meeting ran until midnight,</i></b>

07:47.281 --> 07:49.551
<b><i>but we didn't even decide on anything.</i></b>

07:49.551 --> 07:50.591
<b><i>I'll kill him...</i></b>

07:51.411 --> 07:53.641
<b><i>Or not. Just kidding.</i></b>

07:53.641 --> 07:54.601
<b><i>At times like these...</i></b>

07:55.281 --> 07:56.691
<b><i>There's no better time!</i></b>

07:57.901 --> 07:59.781
<b><i>Tonight, I go see Yamada-san!</i></b>

08:01.181 --> 08:03.861
<b>Here's your change.</b>

08:03.901 --> 08:06.691
<b>droop</b>

08:04.371 --> 08:06.691
<b>Thank you. Come again.</b>

08:07.311 --> 08:08.451
<b>Thank you.</b>

08:11.651 --> 08:15.251
<b><i>I guess Yamada-san's off. 
Or maybe she just finished already.</i></b>

08:15.251 --> 08:17.961
<b><i>Nothing's going my way today.</i></b>

08:19.021 --> 08:22.311
<b><i>I might need a little nicotine pick-me-up.</i></b>

08:23.461 --> 08:25.461
<b>Yikes. Look at that guy.</b>

08:25.731 --> 08:27.951
<b>What a nasty fellow.</b>

08:35.971 --> 08:39.231
<b><i>Wait, they don't have 
a smoking area either?</i></b>

08:39.231 --> 08:40.891
<b>You're kidding me.</b>

08:40.891 --> 08:44.071
<b>Are we smokers that ostracized these days?</b>

08:44.071 --> 08:45.731
<b>Hey, mister.</b>

08:46.381 --> 08:48.511
<b>Over here.</b>

08:53.831 --> 08:56.741
<b>You can light up over here.</b>

08:57.011 --> 08:59.751
<b><i>Whoa! Talk about tempting!</i></b>

08:59.751 --> 09:03.731
<b><i>Wait. Is this the back of the supermarket?</i></b>

09:06.761 --> 09:09.591
<b>Won't you get in trouble for letting 
an outsider use this place?</b>

09:11.181 --> 09:14.891
<b>Relax. Nobody knows who's in or out here.</b>

09:15.811 --> 09:18.721
<b>I guess I'll take you up on that, then.</b>

09:18.721 --> 09:20.421
<b>Sure. Go ahead.</b>

09:34.531 --> 09:37.101
<b><i>I have no idea what kind of look that is,</i></b>

09:37.101 --> 09:39.041
<b><i>but she's got quite 
the striking appearance.</i></b>

09:39.731 --> 09:42.951
<b><i>She looks the furthest thing 
from a supermarket employee.</i></b>

09:45.911 --> 09:51.551
<b>Um, miss? Which section do you work?</b>

09:54.701 --> 09:57.181
<b>C'mon, gimme a light.</b>

09:57.181 --> 09:59.061
<b>That's why I called you back here.</b>

09:59.621 --> 10:01.391
<b>Just say that, then!</b>

10:01.391 --> 10:03.941
<b>Sorry, let my intrusive thoughts win.</b>

10:05.091 --> 10:07.701
<b>Maybe don't do that to a guy you just met.</b>

10:15.251 --> 10:19.531
<b>You're the guy who always lines up 
at register two, aren't you?</b>

10:22.651 --> 10:25.291
<b>Huh, do I? Must be a coincidence.</b>

10:26.111 --> 10:29.921
<b>Coincidence? Even though you line up 
there when the others are free?</b>

10:29.921 --> 10:31.671
<b><i>Caught in 4K!</i></b>

10:32.451 --> 10:34.681
<b>Yamada-san's your favorite, then?</b>

10:35.921 --> 10:38.981
<b><i>She's messing with me on purpose!</i></b>

10:39.941 --> 10:41.631
<b>I get it.</b>

10:41.631 --> 10:43.721
<b>Gotta love Yamada-san, right?</b>

10:44.811 --> 10:47.641
<b>She's pretty and hella stacked,</b>

10:47.641 --> 10:50.421
<b>but you don't get the feeling she's taken.
It's like hitting the jackpot.</b>

10:50.421 --> 10:51.941
<b>You've got it all wrong!</b>

10:51.941 --> 10:56.701
<b>Sure, I may be a creepy guy who 
goes out of his way to line up for her,</b>

10:57.041 --> 11:00.831
<b>but that's just because 
seeing her at work lifts my spirits!</b>

11:01.261 --> 11:03.851
<b>That's the part that feels like 
hitting the jackpot!</b>

11:08.041 --> 11:09.581
<b>I-I'm sorry.</b>

11:09.581 --> 11:11.341
<b>I got too worked up there.</b>

11:13.121 --> 11:14.781
<b>Now I feel better.</b>

11:15.471 --> 11:19.091
<b>I was afraid she had another 
creepo shopper on her hands.</b>

11:19.371 --> 11:23.111
<b>Too many morons come here 
trying to get in her pants.</b>

11:24.961 --> 11:27.931
<b>But you're not one of them, huh?</b>

11:30.181 --> 11:34.281
<b>Try to keep it classy, Sasaki-san.</b>

11:37.921 --> 11:41.501
<b><i>I'd assumed she was the cocky type 
who mocked older men like me for fun,</i></b>

11:41.501 --> 11:44.411
<b><i>but she was actually just a nice girl 
who cares for her coworkers.</i></b>

11:45.031 --> 11:46.091
<b>Hey, uh...</b>

11:47.911 --> 11:50.221
<b>Your bill's ready to pay.</b>

11:50.221 --> 11:52.421
<b>Oh, sorry about that.</b>

11:58.911 --> 12:00.681
<b>Um, Sasaki-san.</b>

12:00.681 --> 12:03.681
<b>Huh? H-How do you know my name?</b>

12:03.971 --> 12:07.581
<b>Oh, I got it from your point card.</b>

12:07.581 --> 12:08.331
<b>Ah...</b>

12:09.431 --> 12:11.061
<b>Thank you. I appreciate it.</b>

12:12.911 --> 12:16.771
<b>I heard from Tayama-chan, 
and it really made me happy.</b>

12:16.771 --> 12:17.491
<b>Huh?</b>

12:17.491 --> 12:20.511
<b>She told me you're a fan of mine.</b>

12:21.571 --> 12:23.611
<b>You dropped this.</b>

12:24.191 --> 12:25.901
<b>Sorry about that.</b>

12:27.981 --> 12:29.831
<b>Thank you. Come again.</b>

12:29.831 --> 12:33.111
<b><i>Damn it, Tayama!</i></b>

12:33.931 --> 12:35.881
<b><i>Now that I know your name, 
you're going down!</i></b>

12:36.571 --> 12:39.091
<b><i>Heyo, it's Tayama.</i></b>

12:45.191 --> 12:47.101
<b>And come to the smoking area again,</b>

12:47.611 --> 12:49.521
<b>Sasaki-san.</b>

12:49.521 --> 12:54.111
<b>Wait, how did <i>Tayama-san</i> know my name?</b>

12:54.851 --> 12:58.481
<b>Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b>

12:58.981 --> 13:02.611
<b>Editing & Typesetting: Geoff Mazzolini
Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b>

13:03.321 --> 13:06.571
<b>Quality Check: Zachary Carlysle
Translation Check: Sho Stifler</b>
